stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NO_HANDLE
    NO_HANDLE --> PAGE_LATCHED_S: acquire pageLatch(S)
    NO_HANDLE --> PAGE_LATCHED_X: acquire pageLatch(X)
    PAGE_LATCHED_S --> CURSOR_ACTIVE: create RecordCursor for read
    PAGE_LATCHED_X --> CURSOR_ACTIVE: create RecordCursor for write
    CURSOR_ACTIVE --> REF_CAPTURED: build IndexRecordRef or IndexGapRef
    REF_CAPTURED --> PAGE_RELEASED: release cursor and page latch before row-lock wait
    PAGE_RELEASED --> WAITING_ROW_LOCK: LockManager wait
    WAITING_ROW_LOCK --> ROW_LOCK_GRANTED: grant
    WAITING_ROW_LOCK --> DEADLOCK_VICTIM: victim
    WAITING_ROW_LOCK --> LOCK_TIMEOUT: timeout
    ROW_LOCK_GRANTED --> RELOCATING: re-enter B+Tree
    RELOCATING --> PAGE_LATCHED_X: reacquire pageLatch(X)
    PAGE_LATCHED_X --> MODIFYING_RECORD: validate ref and modify page body
    MODIFYING_RECORD --> MTR_COMMITTING: collect redo and commit
    MTR_COMMITTING --> RELEASED: release page latch and buffer fix
    DEADLOCK_VICTIM --> RELEASED: rollback releases row locks
    LOCK_TIMEOUT --> RELEASED: statement retry or rollback
    RELEASED --> [*]
